snippet.title: Best Of Michael Blackson 😂 Come Backs, Funniest Disses, & MORE! | Wild 'N Out
snippet.description:
Michael Blackson is no stranger to Wild ‘N Out, from his quick comebacks, to his insane stories, his funny is non-stop! Watch as we take you down memory lane revisiting some of his BEST moments, be sure to comment your favorites below! 😂

#WildNOut #MTV
